{"tid":427848,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有信仰嘅人心靈特別脆弱","createTime":"2017-10-07T16:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T15:41:32.000Z","uid":41229,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8b1dab14973b78262ec14ac5617c14a2488a11b6","tid":427848,"uid":41229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:20:17.000Z","msg":"突然有感而發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得啲人係因為對未知嘅嘢有恐懼<br />\n例如死咗之後嘅世界或者人生意義之類<br />\n跟住就搵個信仰支撐自己嘅內心世界，相信唔同信仰個套泥減少對未知嘅恐懼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以成日覺得d虔誠信徒先係心靈最脆弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為佢地唯一心靈支柱就係信仰，一間突然彈個外星人出黎話你地人類係我地創造嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唸佢地應該會發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地就係啲心靈脆弱接受唔到現實嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有信仰嘅人心靈先堅強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a6f6c1185208635833bda8c95894dbe89ad246","tid":427848,"uid":2419,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:22:32.000Z","msg":"或者掉返轉講 心靈脆弱既人先會有信仰"},{"pid":"9ab8ee7dd882ca63b5043bafab799c2019da1428","tid":427848,"uid":99828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T18:28:09.000Z","msg":"屌你佢地先堅強，乜柒都瀨落佢地個主度<br />\n有外星人嚟實話係主嘅安排"},{"pid":"2bb7ff20220464b4689f03677d1815e2fa483fb8","tid":427848,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T18:30:49.000Z","msg":"滿腦都係啲戇鳩教條、金句<br />\n有咩就拎出黎鼓勵自己<br />\n堅強得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd4f79a9e3e0583150f7ed2ee0a0f4c12794f45","tid":427848,"uid":144718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T18:44:35.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得有信仰嘅人先係最堅強，因為佢哋覺得有個萬能嘅大佬照住，就算有外星人出嚟講啲違反佢哋信仰嘅嘢，佢哋都可以wfc，班撚屌已經比人洗曬腦"},{"pid":"2cdd83a1412f73dbace6b52cedd34d13fd20bd4f","tid":427848,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T18:47:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而覺得有信仰嘅人先係最堅強，因為佢哋覺得有個萬能嘅大佬照住，就算有外星人出嚟講啲違反佢哋信仰嘅嘢，佢哋都可以wfc，班撚屌已經比人洗曬腦</blockquote><br />\n中咗無限月讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94604b919b157c3ae84138707ec83669d394cf4","tid":427848,"uid":113546,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T19:19:11.000Z","msg":"因為脆弱 所以堅強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主講得出喱番說話證明你好膚淺<br />\n<br />\n唔理咩教都好<br />\n能夠認清自己既軟弱 並且願意承認<br />\n喱一份勇氣足以令人堅強"},{"pid":"b645bdaed141a594967ad8f357eefea3d5590d2e","tid":427848,"uid":78500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:41:32.000Z","msg":"啱"}]}